text: Jerzy Dietl (28 April 1927 – 23 February 2021) was a Polish economist and politician. He was a Senator from 1989 until 1991. He was a member of the Civic Parliamentary Club. Dietl was born in Inowrocław, Poland. Dietl died on 23 February 2021 in Warsaw, aged 93.Zmarł Jerzy Dietl, senator I kadencji ==References== Category:1927 births Category:2021 deaths Category:Polish politicians Category:Polish economists
